name: Plaster Tape Gag
description:
I pulled together a small dataset for plaster gags while trying get images for a clear tape gag without stuffing. I didn't manage to find enough to train a Lora for the latter, but decided to give plaster gags a go with what I had. For whatever reason it seems like hires-fix sometimes turns the light white texture to be increasingly faint for the earlier epochs, which sorta recreates the original look I was going for. On testing for this upload I've found it's a lot more finicky than I thought, but I already said I would release it so expect some quirks in your results. Even though it's still a WIP I hope you Enjoy!

Trigger word:

plaster
